    public interface Service<FRAMETYPE extends WindupVertexFrame>

      • frame

        FRAMETYPE frame(org.apache.tinkerpop.gremlin.structure.Vertex vertex)
        Return the given Vertex as a WindupVertexFrame (if possible.)

        Note: This method will always succeed! Even if the given Vertex is not actually the specified WindupVertexFrame type. Call GraphTypeManager.hasType(Class, Vertex) before using this!
